&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Makefile screenshot configured for python3" src="images/Makefile-python3-config-resize.png"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Makefile screenshot configured for python2" src="images/Makefile-python2-config-resize.png"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="pelican"></category><category term="pelican"></category></entry></feed>